creator: Penelope Waller Ulmer
descriptionHtml: Students and SP-Practitioners/Alumni of SPI's professional psychology training program can connect here to register for upcoming group consultation with Penny Waller Ulmer, R. Psych and other fully certified Sensorimotor Psychotherapists / SP Consult Program Interns.  Group Consultation helps Students meet their required hours and helps SP Practitioners connect to explore and improve the application of SP.  Users may meet others to organize peer study groups & peer consult groups, or to register for facilitator-led consultation groups.  Case consultation, skills-drills, and/or role-plays, and support.
title: SP Consulting - Waller Psych
